<!-- views/firm/philosophy.ejs -->
<%- include('../partials/header', {
    pageTitle: pageTitle,
    pageDescription: pageDescription,
    path: path
}) %>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="bg-[#0f2e22] pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-14 md:pb-20 px-6 md:px-16">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
        <span class="font-sans text-sm font-bold text-white/60 uppercase tracking-widest block mb-4">The Firm</span>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white tracking-tight mb-6">Mission &amp; Philosophy</h1>
        <p class="font-sans text-xl text-white/80 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">A partnership forged between brothers at West Point, built on shared values, shared ambition, and a conviction that real estate is the most direct way to leave a lasting mark on the communities we call home.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ MISSION & VISION (2-Column Boxes) ═══════════════ -->
<section class="bg-[#f9f8f6] py-14 md:py-20 px-6 md:px-16">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-0 border border-[#0f2e22]/10">
        <!-- Box 1: Our Mission -->
        <div class="bg-white p-10 md:p-14 border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-[#0f2e22]/10">
            <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] block mb-4">Our Mission</span>
            <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">To acquire and operate residential and commercial communities that generate resilient, yielding cash flow while elevating the resident experience through frictionless, tech-enabled stewardship.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Box 2: Our Vision -->
        <div class="bg-white p-10 md:p-14">
            <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] block mb-4">Our Vision</span>
            <p class="font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">To build a scalable portfolio recognized for operational stability, strict financial transparency, and long-term value creation.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════ BODY SECTIONS (white bg, hr separators) ═══════════════ -->
<section class="bg-white px-6 md:px-16">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">

        <!-- A PARTNERSHIP OF INTENT -->
        <div class="py-10 md:py-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 md:gap-16">
            <div class="md:col-span-4">
                <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-[#0f2e22] leading-tight">A Partnership<br/>of Intent</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-8">
                <div class="prose max-w-none font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
                    <p>Vanier Capital was not conceived in a boardroom. Its founders met as cadets at the <strong>United States Military Academy at West Point</strong>, forging a bond built on shared discipline and purpose. They became not just friends but brothers, a distinction that matters.</p>
                    <p>Following graduation, a reconnection turned into a shared dream: acquiring and developing land to build a place where their families could gather. That simple, personal vision of building a place of one&rsquo;s own is the foundation of the firm.</p>
                    <p>The ambition grew from there. If they could build that for themselves, they could provide it for others. The scope expanded into a clear mandate: improve existing residential housing, develop new residential and commercial properties, and leave a lasting mark on the communities they operate in, not as distant investors, but as people with genuine stakes in the neighborhoods they serve.</p>
                    <p>They say friends make bad business partners. Vanier Capital was founded on the belief that brothers make exceptional ones.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="border-slate-200">

        <!-- THE FIDUCIARY STANDARD -->
        <div class="py-10 md:py-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 md:gap-16">
            <div class="md:col-span-4">
                <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-[#0f2e22] leading-tight">The Fiduciary<br/>Standard</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-8">
                <div class="prose max-w-none font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
                    <p>We do not chase trends. We prioritize principal preservation through conservative leverage and strict underwriting. We decline more opportunities than we pursue, and we refuse to rely on appreciation alone to generate returns.</p>
                    <p>We treat our partners&rsquo; capital with the same scrutiny we apply to our own. Full transparency, conservative assumptions, and no conflicts of interest. Just disciplined acquisition.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="border-slate-200">

        <!-- RESIDENT-FOCUSED OPERATIONS -->
        <div class="py-10 md:py-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 md:gap-16">
            <div class="md:col-span-4">
                <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-[#0f2e22] leading-tight">Resident-Focused<br/>Operations</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-8">
                <div class="prose max-w-none font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
                    <p>We are stewards of assets. Stable, satisfied residents produce stable, predictable cash flow. It is that direct.</p>
                    <p>We prioritize responsive maintenance, transparent lease processes, and capital improvements that matter to the people living in our communities, not cosmetic upgrades designed to look good in a pitch deck.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="border-slate-200">

        <!-- BUILT TO LAST -->
        <div class="py-10 md:py-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 md:gap-16">
            <div class="md:col-span-4">
                <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-[#0f2e22] leading-tight">Built<br/>to Last</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-8">
                <div class="prose max-w-none font-sans text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
                    <p>We are building something we intend to stand behind for a long time. Every acquisition, renovation, and operational decision is weighed against a simple question: <em>will this endure?</em> Not every property will remain in the portfolio forever. That is the nature of the business. But the quality of the work will outlast our ownership of any single asset.</p>
                    <p>Success, for us, is measured by the communities we improve and the commitments we keep. We do what we say we are going to do, and the work speaks for itself.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
